    "description": {
      "value": "<p>        奧法騎士將戰士的武術與嚴謹的魔法研究相結合。他們使用與法師類似的魔法技巧，但只專注於兩個學派:防護和塑能。他們以防護法術保護自身，再以塑能法術同時攻擊多個敵人，因而使其在戰場上更加全面。奧法騎士只能掌握較少的法術，因此只需靠記憶完成而無需使用法術書。</p>\n<p><strong>奧法騎士施法能力Eldritch Knight Spellcasting</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">戰士等級</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">已知戲法</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">已知法術</th>\n<th colspan=\"4\">每環法術位</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>1環</th>\n<th>2環</th>\n<th>3環</th>\n<th>4環</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>3rd</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>4th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>5th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>6th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>7th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>8th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>9th</th>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>10th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>11th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>12th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>13th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>14th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>15th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>16th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>17th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>-</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>18th</th>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>4</td>\